categories: Category:Venator-class Star Destroyers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A Venator-class Star Destroyer was owned by Darth Vader during the reign of the Galactic Empire. He murdered several of the ship's crew, including Admiral Mummert, after being interrupted while meditating in his chamber. By 14 BBY, it had been replaced as Vader's flagship by the Perilous‎.
